// scopeBoxes.manager.json — Scope Box Manager window (Filters-style management surface).
// Command: ScopeBoxManagerCommand. NOTE: action tokens (SetViews/SetDatums/Rename/Delete),
// filter tokens (All/Used/Unused), datum-kind tokens (Grid/Level/RefPlane), and rename
// slot tokens (None/Current Name/Number/Custom) stay as code identifiers.
{
